# Google Sheets API
# 1. Create a project at https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Enable the Google Sheets API
# 3. Create an API Key (restrict it to Sheets API + your domain)
# 4. Make your Google Sheet visible to "Anyone with the link"
# 5. Copy the spreadsheet ID from the URL: docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/SPREADSHEET_ID/edit

SHEETS_API_KEY=your_google_sheets_api_key_here
SHEETS_ID=your_google_spreadsheet_id_here
